window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>She’s my best friend. And I secretly want her.</b></p> <p>Ruby’s my best friend and bandmate. The sister of my good friend, too. Which makes her “triple off-limits” to me. I’d even say she’s like a sister to me, if it weren’t for the unbrotherly dreams I’ve had about her since age sixteen.</p> <p>But when Ruby drunkenly kisses me at a party to piss off her ex, the spark I’ve been working hard to snuff out for years bursts into a raging pyre. And now, I can’t stop obsessing about that kiss and yearning for another one.</p> <p>In fact, after The Kiss That Changed Everything, I’m now determined to do whatever it takes to make Ruby mine, even at the risk of burning my whole world down.</p> <p>Spark is a complete <b>standalone</b>, best friends to lovers, forced proximity, rockstar romance.</p>"; 
